        Static method to convert a given PackagedElement with the type 'uml:Class', 'uml:Interface' or 'uml:Enumeration' to an UmlElement, which will be added to the TemporaryModel Delegates the conversion of Generalizations and InterfaceRealizations to the corresponding GeneralizationConverter or InterfaceRealizationConverter
        Parameters:
        packagedElement - the PackagedElement to convert
        tmpModel - the TemporaryModel to add the converted element to

        Returns:
        the converted UmlElement
